bio.info: Permic is a dragon that was previously a lizard because of an experiment. He's mostly rude and stubborn, but can be nice at times. He has dark red scales, grey fingerless gloves, and pink shoes.
bio.backstory: Permic used to be a lizard, rather than a dragon, for 13 years. Then, just after his 14th birthday, he wandered off to a strange lab. He was dosed with some suspicious medicine, but didn't feel anything, so he went to bed. The next morning, however, he felt different. He had horns on his head and he had gained the ability to breathe fire (He always had the pyrokinesis abilities since he was a lizard dw about that). He had been turned into a dragon. His first reaction was to find a way to get back into his older form, but he hasn't been able to do so. He has gotten used to this new form, however he does still look for ways to get back to his older form.
bio.likes: Training, Hot areas, Messing around with others
bio.dislikes: Those who go mad with power.

bio.info: A tamoan chihuahua who enjoys trouble, is active, and can be overconfident and cocky at times. He has yellow-orange fur, green shoes, and a blue collar. He is mostly clueless about the world around him, but he is eager to explore it more and make friends along the way.
bio.backstory: Sparky's from Planet Tamoa. He has been living in his hometown for 11 years. It has been very peaceful and happy in that hometown, until it was attacked and war broke out. The president of the town instructed the youth to evacuate the planet to a partner planet via an emergency space ship. Sparky's trip was going fine, until the space ship started going out of his control and went crazy, and ended up crashing on the planet called Yaretza. He was seriously injured from the crash but thanks to somebody healing him, he was able to recover. The events still come in his mind at times, but he stays calm and acts like it never happened most of the time.

bio.info: Ira is a shy and timid altarian cat who is very short. She has psychic powers, but they are unstable due to her very young age. She's very kind to those she can trust and is willing to help them out. She has white fur, pink shoes, a purple and pink scarf, and a pale purple dress.
bio.backstory: Ira originally was from Altaria, where she had lived a peaceful(?) life. When war had broken out, she was the first to evacuate. She had no idea where to go, so she had just went to a random planet (which was conveniently(?) the same planet that the group was on).
bio.likes: People whom she can trust, comfortable spots, warmness.

Nightmares, those much larger than her that she doesn't know she can trust
<Instability> Ira's psychic powers are very unstable, and they can often be activated on accident when she's going through a strong emotion. If she were to be forced to constantly abuse her powers with no breaks, she'll enter a phase of pure instability, and if she tries to user her powers in this state, one or more of the following can happen:
- The thing she intended to do (extremely unlikely)
- A harsh psychic attack to a random person
- A harsh psychic attack to everyone around her
- A harsh psychic attack to herself
- Levitating and then dashing into the closest person or a wall
- Telekinesis throwing the closest person or object

bio.info:
A female angel-devil dragon (who was previously a lizard) who is another friend of Permic's (and before anyone assumes, no, not a girlfriend or wife.). She is pretty energetic and extroverted, and loves those who are short and/or cute.
<Appearance (Dragon)> Yanna's current appearance has 2 halves to it. One half has white scales, an angelic wing, short claws, and a half-halo over that half of her head, resembling an angel. However, the other half has black scales, a devil wing, sharp claws, and a horn on that side of her head, resembling a devil. These features had given her unnatural species the name of 'Angel-Devil Dragons.' Asides from those, she has gray shoes, and a short tail.
<Appearance (Lizard)> Yanna's past appearance was not the same as her current appearance. She had gray scales and middle-length claws. And just like her current appearance, she had gray shoes and a short tail. She was also shorter compared to her current form, being 4' if she were still a lizard today.
bio.backstory:
It starts hundreds of years ago, with a Flasheriz dragon and a Darkeriz dragon, named Yango and Yinga respectively. They had completely opposite beliefs, and were pissed off at each other because of that, so, they fought every time they could, in any area they could. This greatly disturbed the deities, who had tried to get them to stop numerous times, but all failed. One day, they all decided enough was enough for the two, and they had decided to curse them. When the two were getting ready for yet another brawl in a cave, they suddenly got stuck to each other (obligatory horny joke goes here), and then had suddenly 
became a black and white orb of liquid; meaning the curse was successful. They couldn't move, nor could they speak. They were just an orb, for hundreds of years...

Now, we skip to 3 years before present day, where Yanna, Permic, and Mike were exploring. They were exploring the cave that Yango and Yinga had gotten cursed. They had then stumbled upon the orb those two were turned into. They did not know what it did or why it was here. Permic and Mike were suspicious and didn't touch it, however Yanna let her curiousity get the best of her, and decided to try and grab the orb. Upon touching the orb, the liquid had entered Yanna's body via her hand. And then, she changed. Her scales changed colors to black on one half and white on the other, her claws on the white half shortened, while on the black half, they sharpened. She had also sprouted an angelic wing on the white half, and a devil wing on the black half, and grew a horn on a black half, while a half-halo sprouted from her head on the white half. Lastly, she grew by two feet and Yango and Yinga both became entities in her mind without a physical form. Yango and Yinga could speak but only Yanna would hear them. Her initial reaction was panicked, and it'd be that way for quite a bit, but she'd settle soon. It's not entirely known what happened after...
bio.likes: Cute/Short people, cute things in general, hanging out with friends
bio.dislikes: People who flex their extraordinary aspects, like intelligence or strength.
